g&h=5c9e4da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老味一百毛又跟風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013638_500f3ef24e398843f5f2ef2cdf681535.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013638_500f3ef24e398843f5f2ef2cdf681535.png&h=376a3f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根本就係香港人犯賤<br />\n憎人富貴厭人窮<br />\n見人屌柒潮語又屌<br />\n但其實自己咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好笑就懶係錄音機咁係咁講<br />\n啱又加唔啱又加<br />\n好似有人俾錢你講咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再係咁香港好快就被同化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學定普通話啦<br />\n所以話香港人冇創意 根本係自己唔用下個腦<br />\n淨係識跟又要善忘得快<br />\n咁會跟風又唔講下689收黑錢？立會主席強推？補選？<br />\n呢啲野又幾日就唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條金魚咁"},{"pid":"154bc8f8ae633426e94fcc6ddec041e738ad1cca","tid":619550,"uid":129039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"彿系"},{"pid":"98c79925392c4de8d1051c5e20354498aca86368","tid":619550,"uid":166264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"154bc8f8ae633426e94fcc6ddec041e738ad1cca","tid":619550,"uid":129039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"彿系"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b14545fb6ec948aa3a90e18a0d1a8e870e21517","tid":619550,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98c79925392c4de8d1051c5e20354498aca86368","tid":619550,"uid":166264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"154bc8f8a