dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改改外國潮圖就做封面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/021409_1b63ed0ad51099e803d3deb920a17a7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F021409_1b63ed0ad51099e803d3deb920a17a7a.png&h=a3bb8cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出處係外國distracted boyfriend <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/021531_a306d02217541879798de63aa8f1e624.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F021531_a306d02217541879798de63aa8f1e624.png&h=e152fae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申以前die hard fan屎<br />\n由黑紙一路追開<br />\n坦白講以前黑紙好睇好多 <br />\n介紹下個artist，有時係政事人物 名人<br />\n講下佢哋有咩灰 有咩理想 呻下火<br />\n再加埋啲看似無厘頭但其實諷刺緊上面講嘅難處嘅10句金句 其實好豐富<br />\n好過宜家個個月100條 睇完都唔知睇左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係咪 發左跡就會失去左味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb036179ec2d025109a268ebcd2b2b76c884251","tid":619550,"uid":139535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cbff6579b38f512b15c692e27081ac549f521635","tid":619550,"uid":166264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"呢幾日好撚多人開口埋口「彿系」「彿系青年」<br />\n彿系呢個term 好撚膠<br />\n個人認為同啲大陸詞語一樣煩膠<br />\n係 彿系 個字係出自日本<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013114_2590930eb2dc1e2e6f7023a3938acfb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013114_2590930eb2dc1e2e6f7023a3938acfb2.png&h=9e37179e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要早係14年就出<br />\n但最近興起咪又係大陸講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013325_25edf532b4ac90b44422c674fdb399fa.p