 />\n呢啲野又幾日就唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條金魚咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"其實最後你知唔知自己講嘢好矛盾 又話跟風又唔跟風 照你例子即係香港人有自己嘅決定思考去跟咩啦"},{"pid":"a53ea20fa082a6a5d6160484ee13ee6b942626fa","tid":619550,"uid":166264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6eb036179ec2d025109a268ebcd2b2b76c884251","tid":619550,"uid":139535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cbff6579b38f512b15c692e27081ac549f521635","tid":619550,"uid":166264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"呢幾日好撚多人開口埋口「彿系」「彿系青年」<br />\n彿系呢個term 好撚膠<br />\n個人認為同啲大陸詞語一樣煩膠<br />\n係 彿系 個字係出自日本<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013114_2590930eb2dc1e2e6f7023a3938acfb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013114_2590930eb2dc1e2e6f7023a3938acfb2.png&h=9e37179e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要早係14年就出<br />\n但最近興起咪又係大陸講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013325_25edf532b4ac90b44422c674fdb399fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013325_25edf532b4ac90b44422c674fdb399fa.png&h=c94ddc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最戇鳩係好多香港媒體，fb page又抄<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013447_5ef99a78313f95d1340c6d7583570dce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013447_5ef99a78313f95d1340c6d7583570dce.png&h=19c74745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013448_8cf6a0e6b5252458ef5189a0f0e8ab1e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013448_8cf6a0e6b5252458ef5189a0f0e8ab1e.png&h=ad411445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013553_ccdc4fd4d90677e45c72eec9ad5f1fd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013553_ccdc4fd4d90677e45c72eec9ad5f1fd3.png&h=5c9e4da4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老味一百毛又跟風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/013638_500f3ef24e398843f5f2ef2cdf681535.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F013638_500f3ef24e398843f5f2ef2cdf681535.png&h=376a3f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根本就係香港人犯賤<br />\n憎人富貴厭人窮<br />\n見人屌柒潮語又屌<br />\n但其實自己咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好笑就懶係錄音機咁係咁講<br />\n啱又加唔啱又加<br />\n好似有人俾錢你講咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再係咁香港好快就被同化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學定普通話啦<br />\n所以話香港人冇創意 根本係自己唔用下個腦<br />\n淨係識跟又要善忘得快<br />\n咁會跟風又唔講下689收黑錢？立會主席強推？補選？<br />\n呢啲野又幾日就唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條金魚咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"其實最後你知唔知自己講嘢好矛盾 又話跟風又唔跟風 照你例子即係香港人有自己嘅決定思考去跟咩啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T18:35:04.000Z","msg":"我冇話香港人冇腦 <br />\n我只係想話啲潮語成日都係咁用好煩膠 <br />\n而唔係焗限係連登厭惡嘅大陸潮語 而係呢個潮語嘅跟風習慣已經不知不覺香港人慣左 從而令創意低下 <br />\n政治等時事嘅關注度都低曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實幾可怕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最恐怖嘅係 其實係邊個決定咩變湖流？<br />\n你真係覺得你有思考能力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係地鐵 fb YouTube 甚至連登講得多而你又跟住講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852aebe417f